    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >欢迎大家加入官方QQ群：779293067 一起交流，反馈bug，提出建议，一起完善游戏。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>游戏特色：</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-广阔的世界地图，处处都有独特的故事</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-丰富的世界观和神话传说</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-交互感十足的战斗系统    </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2382240/extras/bff354a82ac2225098fad113dcc841b9.poster.avif?t=1755038074\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2382240/extras/bff354a82ac2225098fad113dcc841b9.webm?t=1755038074\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2382240/extras/bff354a82ac2225098fad113dcc841b9.mp4?t=1755038074\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong>游戏玩法：</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >本游戏是一款横版类银河恶魔城冒险游戏，以刀剑争锋的冷兵器战斗为玩法核心。你的任务是穿过广阔的王国，结识新的朋友，遇见新的敌人，与诸多身形可怕的Boss交战，并通过提升等级来强化角色的能力。     <br>    <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2382240/extras/fb001ae38cbe8bc1e145df27115ec2e8.poster.avif?t=1755038074\" width=650 height=366 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2382240/extras/fb001ae38cbe8bc1e145df27115ec2e8.webm?t=1755038074\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2382240/extras/fb001ae38cbe8bc1e145df27115ec2e8.mp4?t=1755038074\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong>游戏故事：</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在被遗忘国度的一个偏远村庄里，生活着一个默默无闻的女孩，艾维塔。然而，一场可怕的疫病袭击了她的家园，所有人都认为末日降临了。艾维塔不愿接受这种绝望的想法，她拿起离剑，披上战甲，毅然决然地踏上寻找治疗方法的旅程，去探索国度内未曾涉足的广袤区域。她在冒险中将会遇见从未见过的风景，拜访其他的村落，结识朋友，击败敌人，她不只是在寻找治病良方，更是给所有人带来一缕希望的曙光。</p>",
